Package: pems.utils
Title: Portable Emissions (and Other Mobile) Measurement System
        Utilities
Version: 0.3.0.7
Date: 2024-12-28
Description: Utility functions for the handling, analysis and
        visualisation of data from portable emissions measurement
        systems ('PEMS') and other similar mobile activity monitoring
        devices. The package includes a dedicated 'pems' data class
        that manages many of the quality control, unit handling and
        data archiving issues that can hinder efforts to standardise
        'PEMS' research.
